                id, device_id, transaction_type, amount, currency,
                status, encrypted_pin_block, ksn, card_number_masked,
                merchant_id, terminal_id, authorization_code,
                response_code, response_message, created_at, updated_at
            )
            VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
